text: Carena may refer to: * Carena, Ticino, a hamlet within the municipality of Sant'Antonio in the Swiss canton of Ticino * Carena (trademark), a trademark for the drug Aminophylline * Felice Carena, an Italian painter * Marcela Carena, an Argentinian theoretical physicist * Punta Carena Lighthouse, a lighthouse on the Italian island of Capri
